{
 "name": "RPlog_Mira_s_First_Lesson",
 "title": "Mira's First Lesson",
 "summary": "Aboard a ship, the dark-side adept Simon Sezirok begins teaching the eccentric young Mira to use the Force, building on her childlike belief that her 'Tivian jumping beans' are magic. Using a screw and then a handful of rocks as props, Simon demonstrates that inanimate objects will move at his will just as her beans do, gently leading her toward the realization that belief shapes what is possible. Mira, stubborn and literal, insists rocks cannot jump but is rattled when Simon makes them hop, and she manages to coax her beans to jump on command. Tiring of the strange lesson, Mira withdraws to rest, and Simon, uncertain whether his unorthodox method is working, sends his student off with a reminder that mastery of the body leads to mastery of the mind.",
